1. in Article 2, the date ‘31 December 2010’ is replaced by ‘31 December 2011’;
2. Article 3 is amended as follows:
(a) in the introductory phrase, the date ‘31 December 2010’ is replaced by ‘31 December 2011’;
(b) point (c) is deleted;
3. in Article 4(1), the introductory phrase is replaced by the following:
4. in Article 5(2), the date ‘31 October 2010’ is replaced by ‘31 October 2011’;
